### case 1 add product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 40 Running Shoes",
  "sku": "NIKE-PEG40-RUN",
  "description": "Lightweight and responsive running shoes designed for everyday training with breathable mesh and Zoom Air cushioning.",
  "price": 129.99,
  "weight": 0.28,
  "barcode": "196149357892",
  "categoryId": "a7913525-c02e-4777-bfb7-8bdecdfd5d1e"
}


### case 2 get product by product id
GET  http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/b97e8c81-d962-404a-aa9e-00c009b09f35
Content-Type: application/json

### case 3 get product by sku id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/sku/NIKE-PEG40-RUN
Content-Type: application/json

