### case 7 soft delete product
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/b97e8c81-d962-404a-aa9e-00c009b09f35
Content-Type: application/json

### case 8 Activate product
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/b97e8c81-d962-404a-aa9e-00c009b09f35/activate
Content-Type: application/json
